    "Profit or loss for this trade calculated using LIFO (Last-In, First-Out) cost basis — the closing trade is matched against the most recently opened position. Differs from average-cost PnL and is often used for tax-lot or short-term-focused accounting." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "使用后进先出（LIFO）成本法计算的单笔盈亏——平仓交易与最近一次开仓的持仓相匹配。与按平均成本计算的盈亏不同，常用于税务批次核算或侧重短期的分析。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Profit or loss from closed positions only — the cash actually gained or lost from trades where both entry and exit were executed." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "仅来自已平仓位的盈亏——即入场和出场均已执行的交易所实际获得或损失的现金。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Profit or loss from passively buying at the start and holding until the end over the same period. Used as a benchmark — if Total PnL exceeds this, the active strategy outperformed buy-and-hold." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "在同一期间内被动买入并持有至结束所产生的盈亏。用作基准——若总盈亏超过此值，则主动策略跑赢了买入并持有。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
