      }
    },
    "Technical Indicators" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "技术指标"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The date and time when this backtest was executed. Useful for distinguishing between multiple runs of the same strategy." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此回测的执行日期和时间。用于区分同一策略的多次运行。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The largest peak-to-trough decline in portfolio value during the period. A key measure of downside risk — shows the worst loss an investor would have had to endure." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "期间内投资组合价值从峰值到谷底的最大回撤。衡量下行风险的关键指标——显示投资者可能承受的最大损失。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The largest profit earned on a single trade during the period. Highlights the best individual trade outcome." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "期间内单笔交易的最大利润。突出显示最佳的单笔交易结果。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The number of closed trade pairs that ended with a loss." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "以亏损收尾的已平仓交易对数量。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The number of closed trade pairs that ended with a profit." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "以盈利收尾的已平仓交易对数量。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The number of matched entry-and-exit trade pairs. A trade pair consists of an opening trade and its corresponding closing trade, and is the unit used to measure PnL and win rate." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "已配对的入场与出场交易数量。一个交易对由开仓交易及其对应的平仓交易组成，是衡量盈亏和胜率的基本单位。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The percentage of closed trade pairs that were profitable (Winning Trades ÷ Total Trade Pairs). A high win rate alone does not guarantee profitability — a few large losses can outweigh many small wins." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "已平仓交易对中盈利的比例（盈利交易 ÷ 总交易对）。高胜率本身并不能保证盈利——少数大额亏损可能抵消许多小额盈利。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The selected result could not be loaded" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "无法加载所选结果"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The selected trading run could not be found" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "无法找到所选的交易运行"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The Sharpe Ratio measures risk-adjusted return. It shows how much excess return you receive for the extra volatility of holding a riskier asset.\n\nA negative ratio (%@) indicates the strategy is underperforming the risk-free rate. Consider reviewing the strategy's risk management." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "夏普比率衡量风险调整后收益。它显示了您为持有风险较高资产所承受的额外波动率，能换取多少超额收益。\n\n负比率（%@）表明该策略跑输无风险利率。请考虑审查该策略的风险管理。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The Sharpe Ratio measures risk-adjusted return. It shows how much excess return you receive for the extra volatility of holding a riskier asset.\n\nA ratio above 3.0 (%@) indicates excellent risk-adjusted performance. This is exceptional, but verify it's sustainable and not due to overfitting." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "夏普比率衡量风险调整后收益。它显示了您为持有风险较高资产所承受的额外波动率，能换取多少超额收益。\n\n比率高于3.0（%@）表明风险调整后的表现极佳。这非常优异，但请验证其是否具有可持续性，且不是由于过拟合所致。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The Sharpe Ratio measures risk-adjusted return. It shows how much excess return you receive for the extra volatility of holding a riskier asset.\n\nA ratio below 1.0 (%@) suggests suboptimal risk-adjusted returns. The returns may not adequately compensate for the risk taken." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "夏普比率衡量风险调整后收益。它显示了您为持有风险较高资产所承受的额外波动率，能换取多少超额收益。\n\n比率低于1.0（%@）表明风险调整后收益欠佳。收益可能无法充分补偿所承担的风险。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The Sharpe Ratio measures risk-adjusted return. It shows how much excess return you receive for the extra volatility of holding a riskier asset.\n\nA ratio between 1.0-2.0 (%@) indicates acceptable risk-adjusted performance. This is considered decent for most strategies." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "夏普比率衡量风险调整后收益。它显示了您为持有风险较高资产所承受的额外波动率，能换取多少超额收益。\n\n比率介于1.0-2.0之间（%@）表明风险调整后的表现尚可。对于大多数策略而言，这已相当不错。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The Sharpe Ratio measures risk-adjusted return. It shows how much excess return you receive for the extra volatility of holding a riskier asset.\n\nA ratio between 2.0-3.0 (%@) indicates very good risk-adjusted performance. The strategy is generating strong returns relative to its risk." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "夏普比率衡量风险调整后收益。它显示了您为持有风险较高资产所承受的额外波动率，能换取多少超额收益。\n\n比率介于2.0-3.0之间（%@）表明风险调整后的表现非常好。相对于所承担的风险，该策略正在产生强劲的收益。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This result does not contain monthly statistics or percentile data." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此结果不包含月度统计或百分位数数据。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Ticker" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "交易代码"
          }
        }
      }
