    "Title" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "标题"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Total capital deployed across all trades during the period. Represents the cumulative cost basis used by the strategy to enter positions." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "期间内所有交易投入的总资金。代表该策略进入仓位所使用的累计成本基础。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Total Fees" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "总费用"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Total Investment" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "总投资"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Total Items: %lld" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "项目总数：%lld"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Total PnL" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "总盈亏"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Total Profit and Loss across all trades — realized PnL plus unrealized PnL on any open positions.\n\nResults are close to buy-and-hold (difference: %@). Make sure the active-trading overhead — fees, slippage, effort — is worth it." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "所有交易的总盈亏——已实现盈亏加上未平仓位的未实现盈亏。\n\n结果与买入并持有相近（差额：%@）。请确保主动交易的开销——手续费、滑点、精力——值得付出。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Total Profit and Loss across all trades — realized PnL plus unrealized PnL on any open positions.\n\nThe strategy outperformed buy-and-hold by %@. The strategy is adding value over passive holding." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "所有交易的总盈亏——已实现盈亏加上未平仓位的未实现盈亏。\n\n该策略跑赢买入并持有 %@。相较于被动持有，该策略正在创造超额价值。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Total Profit and Loss across all trades — realized PnL plus unrealized PnL on any open positions.\n\nThe strategy significantly outperformed buy-and-hold by %@. Strong alpha — verify this isn't due to a single lucky period or overfitting." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "所有交易的总盈亏——已实现盈亏加上未平仓位的未实现盈亏。\n\n该策略显著跑赢买入并持有 %@。强劲的超额收益——但请核实这并非源于某一次幸运行情或过拟合。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Total Profit and Loss across all trades — realized PnL plus unrealized PnL on any open positions.\n\nThe strategy significantly underperformed buy-and-hold by %@. Passive holding would have produced a far better outcome over this period." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "所有交易的总盈亏——已实现盈亏加上未平仓位的未实现盈亏。\n\n该策略显著跑输买入并持有 %@。在此期间被动持有本可获得好得多的结果。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Total Profit and Loss across all trades — realized PnL plus unrealized PnL on any open positions.\n\nThe strategy underperformed buy-and-hold by %@. Consider whether active trading is justified versus simply holding." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "所有交易的总盈亏——已实现盈亏加上未平仓位的未实现盈亏。\n\n该策略跑输买入并持有 %@。请考虑相较于简单持有，主动交易是否值得。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Total Profit and Loss across all trades. Combines realized PnL from closed positions and unrealized PnL from any positions still open at the end of the period." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "所有交易的总盈亏。合并已平仓位的已实现盈亏和期末未平仓位的未实现盈亏。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Total Profit and Loss expressed as a percentage of total invested capital. Useful for comparing strategies that deploy different amounts of capital." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "总盈亏占总投入资金的百分比。便于比较使用不同资金量的策略。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
